title: Azizi
name: Azizi
description:
Azizi Developments is a leading real estate and lifestyle developer in Dubai, UAE. The private company Azizi was founded in 2007 and has successfully developed and commissioned thousands of properties in various prestigious areas of Dubai. Azizi's main project locations include Al Furjan, near Expo 2020, Meydan (MBR City), near downtown Dubai, Dubai Healthcare City, Palm Jumeirah, Downtown Jebel Ali, Studio City and Sports City. Azizi is proud of its extensive portfolio of modern residential and mixed-use complexes strategically located in some of the most sought-after areas of Dubai. Applying a proactive, transparent and construction-oriented approach, Azizi strives to meet and exceed expectations by offering value for money and ensuring customer orientation.

Azizi has a diverse local and international client base, including investors and end users (owner-occupiers), which cover more than 100 nationalities. Azizi's head office, located in the center of Dubai on Sheikh Zayed Street, employs more than 1,200 people representing more than 50 different nationalities. Currently, Azizi has about 100 ongoing projects to be implemented between 2021 and 2023, and more than 100 additional projects at the planning stage worth several billion US dollars, which are projected to be completed between 2023 and 2025. From value-oriented middle-income residential neighborhoods with shops and bed and breakfast establishments to luxurious coastal villages on Palm Jumeirah for the most discerning, Azizi offers a diverse portfolio for every taste and budget.

title: Nakheel
name: Nakheel
description:
Based in Dubai, Nakheel is a leading global developer whose innovative, iconic projects form an iconic portfolio of master communities and residential, retail, hotel and leisure facilities that are crucial to realizing Dubai's vision. Nakheel's coastal projects, including the world-renowned, award-winning Palm Jumeirah, have added more than 300 kilometers to Dubai's original 70-kilometer coastline, paving the way for the construction of hundreds of beachfront homes, resorts, hotels and attractions.

Nakheel's main developments cover 15,000 hectares, accommodate almost 300,000 people and provide a growing range of destinations, attractions and amenities for Dubai citizens, residents and tourists. These include Palm Jumeirah, The World, Jumeirah Islands, Jumeirah Park, Jumeirah Village, Al Furjan, Gardens, Discovery Gardens, Jebel Ali Village, Dragon City, Villas Over Al Shiba, Varsan Village, International City and Dubai Islands under construction - a new destination for tourism, life and leisure in the oldest, most traditional shopping mall in Dubai.

title: Select Group
name: Select Group
description:
Select Group company is a diversified company based in Dubai, United Arab Emirates with proved competences in real estate development, investments, hospitality and retail.

Established in 2002, the Select Group developer has many residential, commercial and mixed-use developments across the United Arab Emirates, Saudi Arabia, Europe and the UK.

The most famous projects of Select Group are Marina Gate, Studio One and The Torch in Dubai Marina. The Group‚Äôs first project in Dubai was The Torch, which was the tallest residential tower in the world at the time of its completion in May 2011.

The founder and CEO of Select Group is Rahail Aslam. With the lead of Rahail the company has delivered 5.5M sq. ft of development in Dubai and has 7M sq. ft in progress to date.

After the successful launch of Marina Gate in 2014 Select Group has proved itself as one of the leading private real estate company in the United Arab Emirates.

title: Golden Woods
name: Golden Woods
description:
Golden Woods Real Estate Development is a reputable family-owned business that was established in 2013 and is headquartered in Dubai. Specializing in a diverse range of exceptional projects, the company is committed to excellence by blending innovation and expertise to produce inspiring and enduring spaces. With a foundation built on trust, quality, and an unwavering dedication to delivering superior results, Golden Woods Real Estate Development has created a legacy that speaks for itself.

Led by the CEO, the company's focus is on crafting spaces where exceptional design seamlessly merges with functionality, resulting in environments that not only inspire but also stand the test of time. Their core values revolve around integrity, innovation, and a pursuit of excellence in every aspect of their operations.

Customer satisfaction remains paramount in every project undertaken, with a track record of continually surpassing client expectations. Utilizing over a decade of experience in real estate development, Golden Woods Real Estate Development has successfully completed numerous landmark projects, showcasing their expertise and unwavering commitment to their clients.

Emphasizing sustainability, the company is dedicated to incorporating environmentally conscious practices into their developments, ensuring they cater to current needs while simultaneously laying the groundwork for a sustainable future for generations to come.

The CEO, Arif MALIA, encapsulates the company's mission of setting new benchmarks of excellence and delivering significant value to clients and communities. By prioritizing trust and fostering enduring relationships, Golden Woods Real Estate Development continues to stay ahead of market trends by offering innovative solutions tailored to the evolving demands of the industry. Their projects are designed to surpass expectations by marrying exceptional quality with a positive and lasting impact on the communities they serve.

Golden Woods Real Estate Development invites all stakeholders to join them in shaping the future, with a collective effort towards creating developments that inspire, endure, and drive mutual success.

title: Wadan Developments
name: Wadan Developments
description:
WADAN Developments is a fast-growing real estate developer in Dubai, established in 2025. We create homes that are more than just beautiful spaces ‚Äî they are designed to bring comfort, wellness, and smart technology together.

Our team has international experience in Qatar, Pakistan, and Afghanistan. We also own Autolink Contracting (ALC), our in-house construction company with almost 30 years of experience, its own equipment, and skilled workers. This means we control the quality, speed, and costs of every project. Our track record includes working on world-famous projects such as the FIFA World Cup 2022 stadiums in Qatar, Lusail City, Katara Towers, and luxury hotels under brands like Radisson Blu, Hilton, and Rotana.

Every WADAN home comes fully furnished with smart home technology, AI-powered personalization, and wellness features like air purification, aromatherapy, and circadian lighting.

We carefully choose prime locations that offer the right balance of price, value, and lifestyle ‚Äî ensuring both homeowners and investors can benefit. Our payment plans are designed to suit both, offering great value and strong return on investment.

By combining smart design, global expertise, and a hospitality-inspired approach, WADAN Developments is building a new standard of luxury living in Dubai ‚Äî homes that truly deliver a vision beyond luxury.

title: AMWAJ Development
name: AMWAJ Development
description:
AMWAJ Development is a leading real estate developer in Dubai, pursuing its mission to provide innovative and environmentally friendly development solutions. With a focus on excellence and quality, AMWAJ Development strives to enhance the quality of life for both residents and visitors while making a positive contribution to the local community.

AMWAJ Development is backed by an experienced founder and leadership team with over 25 years of diverse international experience, including 11 years specifically dedicated to property development in Europe and the Middle East. AMWAJ Development specializes in the development and sale of residential and commercial projects, aiming to create modern, premium, family-oriented living spaces in Dubai's most sought-after areas.

Our mission is to reimagine Dubai's real estate environment by delivering innovative and sustainable development solutions that set new standards for the quality of urban living. We are committed to creating iconic landmarks that offer luxurious, contemporary living spaces with high-quality finishes and the integration of smart technology. We aim to lead the way in creating vibrant spaces that enhance living standards and offer diversity, redefining urban living in Dubai and beyond.

Our core values drive us to undertake projects that reflect our commitment to quality and the well-being of society.

title: Dubai Properties
name: Dubai Properties
description:
Dubai Properties made a significant impact in 2016 by delivering over 3,000 residential units, with 2,900 of these located in the fast-growing Dubailand area, and 124 units nestled in the upscale Dubai Wharf. Each project reflects the developer's commitment to quality and the enhancement of urban living experiences.

In a groundbreaking move, Dubai Properties introduced their innovative water homes at Marasi Business Bay in September 2017, with the first collection of these luxurious floating residences arriving all the way from Finland. This milestone highlights the developer‚Äôs dedication to bringing unique living concepts to Dubai's vibrant real estate market.

Further expanding its portfolio, Dubai Properties also launched Riverside, a stunning 420-unit residential tower along the picturesque Dubai Water Canal. As the first of four planned Marasi towers, Riverside marks the beginning of an exciting new chapter in Business Bay, redefining waterfront living in the heart of the city.

title: Bonyan International Investment Group
name: Bonyan International Investment Group
description:
Bonyan Group has been a pioneering force in developing the lucrative real estate market in the Gulf and MENA regions. Since entering the real estate market in 2002, which ultimately lead to the successful creation of Bonyan International Investment Group (Holding), the Company, along with its partners, co-founders and subsidiaries, has been successfully and steadily growing and developing, acquiring a prestigious reputation in the region and establishing offices in the United Arab Emirates, in Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ajman, Al Ain, Ras Al Khaimah, Jordan, Qatar, Oman, the British Virgin Islands, the Bahamas, the Cayman Islands and many other countries.¬†

Our success is attributed to providing professional support through our staff, along with the support received by Bonyan Group and its customers. Whether taking on total ownership of a development project, or acting as partners, we offer well-established trusted expertise in every conceivable area including master planning for start-ups. This includes land planning, project development and management; investment; trading; real estate brokerage, renting and leasing.¬†

Over the years, Bonyan Group has been seeking access to the real estate development integration through linking all the real estate development stages with experienced and competent consultation, engineering, finance and investment firms and offices and with all relevant real estate development processes, including the development and management of cities and towers and marketing of its units, resulting in creating its distinctive partnerships and organizations, listed below in Our Stakeholders and Related Companies.

title: Swiss Property
name: Swiss Property
description:
Swiss real estate strives for perfection. We work in the center of the culture of excellence and promotion to ensure the highest standard of management.

Every improvement made with an eye to what needs to happen is an enterprise of lasting value. We combine earthly attractions and amenities as much as could be expected to guarantee a more favorable lifestyle for the majority of our residents. Equally important is that each property should be one of a kind, in many ways the same as the general population that lives in it.

Our main goal is to set standards of splendor in the land business by providing exquisite properties that interest people who value craftsmanship, development and maintainability.

As an organization, we strive to create both respect and splendor by providing our clients with prime real estate and offsetting budget returns to our financial professionals. Honed methodology, respectability and the pursuit of greatness are part of the ideas shared by all Swiss Property group employees.

title: Al Habtoor Group
name: Al Habtoor Group
description:
Al Habtoor Grouphas grown with the United Arab Emirates. What started out as a small engineering firm in 1970, is today one of the region‚Äôs most respected conglomerates with interests in the hospitality, automotive, real estate, education and publishing sectors. The Al Habtoor Group has earned itself a solid reputation both locally and internationally due to the vision of its Chairman, Khalaf Ahmad Al Habtoor.

The Al Habtoor Group is one of the UAE's most respected and successful businesses. Today it operates in the UAE and international markets. It employs thousands of highly-qualified, experienced professionals. Just as the name of the UAE has become synonymous with trade and enterprise all over the world, the name of the Al Habtoor Group has become synonymous with dynamic growth, evidenced by its commitment to develop and grow businesses in multiple sectors.

It proudly waves the United Arab Emirates flag in many cities around the globe including London, Vienna, Budapest, Beirut and Springfield, Illinois.

The Group‚Äôs hospitality division includes 14 world-class hotels; seven locally and seven abroad. The portfolio includes:

Dubai, United Arab Emirates

  • Habtoor Grand Resort
  • Waldorf Astoria Dubai Palm Jumeirah
  • Habtoor Palace, LXR Hotels & Resorts
  • V Hotel, Curio Collection by Hilton
  • Hilton Dubai Al Habtoor City
  • Metropolitan Hotel Dubai
  • Al Habtoor Polo Resort

Overseas

  • Imperial Hotel, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Vienna (Austria)
  • Hilton London Wembley (United Kingdom)
  • Hilton Beirut Habtoor Grand (Lebanon)
  • Hilton Beirut Metropolitan Palace (Lebanon)
  • President Abraham Lincoln Springfield ‚Äì a DoubleTree by Hilton Hotel (United States)
  • InterContinental Budapest (Hungary)
  • The Ritz-Carlton, Budapest (Hungary)

Al Habtoor Motors' brand portfolio includes Mitsubishi, with a wide choice of sedans, 4x4's and commercial vehicles, two well-known Chinese brands, JAC and Chery, Temsa buses as well as premium marques such as Bentley, McLaren and Bugatti.

The company has a well-established network of nine showrooms, nine service centres, four body shops and ten parts centres that effectively cover the entire UAE. In 2015, Al Habtoor Motors entered the Saudi Arabian market for the first time with Mitsubishi Fuso.

Al Habtoor Motors owns and operates the world‚Äôs first ‚Äì and largest ‚Äì iconic Bentley Motors showroom to be built in major cities around the world. The state-of-the-art showroom is located in a prime location on Sheikh Zayed Road, with built-up area of 76,000 square feet. It consists of three basement floors designated for parking, in addition to three floors of customer area displaying over 70 vehicles, offices, boutiques, Mulliner lounge, a VIP Majlis and other related required services. Adding to its unique design, over 200 thousand LED lights illuminate the outer fa√ßade.

Diamondlease specialises in short-term and long-term leasing of popular brands ranging from small to mid-sized saloons to pick-up trucks and buses.

The Group‚Äôs real estate division includes a variety of commercial and residential properties from office space to luxury villas. Al Habtoor Real Estate provides a total value package, with an emphasis on client needs.

The real estate division includes Al Habtoor City‚Äôs Residence Collection, currently under development. The upmarket lifestyle destination embodies exclusivity and style. The three residential towers comprise of deluxe apartments, lofts and penthouses, ranging from 1-7 bedrooms in a unique neighbourhood. Residents will have access to all Al Habtoor City‚Äôs amenities, which include the largest swimming pool podium in the UAE, a state-of-the-art gym, luxury spa, signature restaurants and have the added bonus of all being right on the banks of the Dubai Water Canal. In addition they can benefit from three five-star hotels right on their doorstep.

The Al Habtoor Group has long been a pioneer in the field of education, it operates two well-established schools offering quality education from KG1 to Grade 13. Emirates International School ‚Äì Jumeirah and Emirates International School ‚Äì The Meadows are accredited IB World Schools.

The Group‚Äôs publishing arm regularly produces quality publications including Al Shindagah magazine, a bilingual corporate magazine, which has been in circulation since1993.

title: Pasha 1
name: Pasha 1
description:
Pasha1 is a Dubai-based real estate developer born from the long-standing legacy of PJS Global, a family business with over four decades of success in international trade, agro-processing, logistics, industrial ventures and asset management. Backed by operations in nine countries, fourteen offices and strong financial capability, the group‚Äôs expansion into real estate represents a strategic evolution built on trust, operational excellence and global experience. The new venture is led by the second and third generation of the Jain family, combining heritage with a forward-looking vision.

The company is driven by the leadership of Pulkit Jain and Parshva Jain, who bring together international expertise, disciplined management and a focus on well-designed living environments. Pasha1 builds on the core values of PJS Global, emphasising transparency, long-term partnerships and community development. Its debut project, Stax in Jumeirah Village Circle, reflects the brand‚Äôs philosophy of design, functionality and lifestyle tailored to modern residents and investors.

Pasha1 positions itself to shape the future of Dubai‚Äôs residential landscape. The developer focuses on quality architecture, sustainability and integration within the urban fabric, creating developments that deliver value through liveable spaces, strong communities and long-term growth.

title: New MFOUR Real Estate Development
name: New MFOUR Real Estate Development
description:
Founded in 2010, MFOUR Development has grown from a construction contracting firm into a leading real estate developer, delivering landmark projects across Mumbai and Pune, including Aura Heights and Ocean View. The renowned company is expanding into Dubai with the debut of a premium, mid-rise residential development in Jumeirah Gardens.

MFOUR also excels in construction, offering comprehensive EPC (Engineering, Procurement, Construction) and LSTK (Lump Sum Turnkey) project execution and civil construction services. The hospitality division of MFOUR also operates luxury hotels in Dubai and Istanbul.

title: Swiss Property
name: Swiss Property
description:
Swiss real estate strives for perfection. We work in the center of the culture of excellence and promotion to ensure the highest standard of management.

Every improvement made with an eye to what needs to happen is an enterprise of lasting value. We combine earthly attractions and amenities as much as could be expected to guarantee a more favorable lifestyle for the majority of our residents. Equally important is that each property should be one of a kind, in many ways the same as the general population that lives in it.

Our main goal is to set standards of splendor in the land business by providing exquisite properties that interest people who value craftsmanship, development and maintainability.

As an organization, we strive to create both respect and splendor by providing our clients with prime real estate and offsetting budget returns to our financial professionals. Honed methodology, respectability and the pursuit of greatness are part of the ideas shared by all Swiss Property group employees.

title: Swiss Property
name: Swiss Property
description:
Swiss real estate strives for perfection. We work in the center of the culture of excellence and promotion to ensure the highest standard of management.

Every improvement made with an eye to what needs to happen is an enterprise of lasting value. We combine earthly attractions and amenities as much as could be expected to guarantee a more favorable lifestyle for the majority of our residents. Equally important is that each property should be one of a kind, in many ways the same as the general population that lives in it.

Our main goal is to set standards of splendor in the land business by providing exquisite properties that interest people who value craftsmanship, development and maintainability.

As an organization, we strive to create both respect and splendor by providing our clients with prime real estate and offsetting budget returns to our financial professionals. Honed methodology, respectability and the pursuit of greatness are part of the ideas shared by all Swiss Property group employees.

title: Al Habtoor Group
name: Al Habtoor Group
description:
Al Habtoor Grouphas grown with the United Arab Emirates. What started out as a small engineering firm in 1970, is today one of the region‚Äôs most respected conglomerates with interests in the hospitality, automotive, real estate, education and publishing sectors. The Al Habtoor Group has earned itself a solid reputation both locally and internationally due to the vision of its Chairman, Khalaf Ahmad Al Habtoor.

The Al Habtoor Group is one of the UAE's most respected and successful businesses. Today it operates in the UAE and international markets. It employs thousands of highly-qualified, experienced professionals. Just as the name of the UAE has become synonymous with trade and enterprise all over the world, the name of the Al Habtoor Group has become synonymous with dynamic growth, evidenced by its commitment to develop and grow businesses in multiple sectors.

It proudly waves the United Arab Emirates flag in many cities around the globe including London, Vienna, Budapest, Beirut and Springfield, Illinois.

The Group‚Äôs hospitality division includes 14 world-class hotels; seven locally and seven abroad. The portfolio includes:

Dubai, United Arab Emirates

  • Habtoor Grand Resort
  • Waldorf Astoria Dubai Palm Jumeirah
  • Habtoor Palace, LXR Hotels & Resorts
  • V Hotel, Curio Collection by Hilton
  • Hilton Dubai Al Habtoor City
  • Metropolitan Hotel Dubai
  • Al Habtoor Polo Resort

Overseas

  • Imperial Hotel, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Vienna (Austria)
  • Hilton London Wembley (United Kingdom)
  • Hilton Beirut Habtoor Grand (Lebanon)
  • Hilton Beirut Metropolitan Palace (Lebanon)
  • President Abraham Lincoln Springfield ‚Äì a DoubleTree by Hilton Hotel (United States)
  • InterContinental Budapest (Hungary)
  • The Ritz-Carlton, Budapest (Hungary)

Al Habtoor Motors' brand portfolio includes Mitsubishi, with a wide choice of sedans, 4x4's and commercial vehicles, two well-known Chinese brands, JAC and Chery, Temsa buses as well as premium marques such as Bentley, McLaren and Bugatti.

The company has a well-established network of nine showrooms, nine service centres, four body shops and ten parts centres that effectively cover the entire UAE. In 2015, Al Habtoor Motors entered the Saudi Arabian market for the first time with Mitsubishi Fuso.

Al Habtoor Motors owns and operates the world‚Äôs first ‚Äì and largest ‚Äì iconic Bentley Motors showroom to be built in major cities around the world. The state-of-the-art showroom is located in a prime location on Sheikh Zayed Road, with built-up area of 76,000 square feet. It consists of three basement floors designated for parking, in addition to three floors of customer area displaying over 70 vehicles, offices, boutiques, Mulliner lounge, a VIP Majlis and other related required services. Adding to its unique design, over 200 thousand LED lights illuminate the outer fa√ßade.

Diamondlease specialises in short-term and long-term leasing of popular brands ranging from small to mid-sized saloons to pick-up trucks and buses.

The Group‚Äôs real estate division includes a variety of commercial and residential properties from office space to luxury villas. Al Habtoor Real Estate provides a total value package, with an emphasis on client needs.

The real estate division includes Al Habtoor City‚Äôs Residence Collection, currently under development. The upmarket lifestyle destination embodies exclusivity and style. The three residential towers comprise of deluxe apartments, lofts and penthouses, ranging from 1-7 bedrooms in a unique neighbourhood. Residents will have access to all Al Habtoor City‚Äôs amenities, which include the largest swimming pool podium in the UAE, a state-of-the-art gym, luxury spa, signature restaurants and have the added bonus of all being right on the banks of the Dubai Water Canal. In addition they can benefit from three five-star hotels right on their doorstep.

The Al Habtoor Group has long been a pioneer in the field of education, it operates two well-established schools offering quality education from KG1 to Grade 13. Emirates International School ‚Äì Jumeirah and Emirates International School ‚Äì The Meadows are accredited IB World Schools.

The Group‚Äôs publishing arm regularly produces quality publications including Al Shindagah magazine, a bilingual corporate magazine, which has been in circulation since1993.

The Al Habtoor Group has earned itself a solid reputation both locally and internationally due to the vision of its Chairman, Khalaf Ahmad Al Habtoor.

The Al Habtoor Group is one of the UAE's most respected and successful businesses. Today it operates in the UAE and international markets. It employs thousands of highly-qualified, experienced professionals. Just as the name of the UAE has become synonymous with trade and enterprise all over the world, the name of the Al Habtoor Group has become synonymous with dynamic growth, evidenced by its commitment to develop and grow businesses in multiple sectors.

It proudly waves the United Arab Emirates flag in many cities around the globe including London, Vienna, Budapest, Beirut and Springfield, Illinois.

The Group‚Äôs hospitality division includes 14 world-class hotels; seven locally and seven abroad. The portfolio includes:

Dubai, United Arab Emirates

  • Habtoor Grand Resort
  • Waldorf Astoria Dubai Palm Jumeirah
  • Habtoor Palace, LXR Hotels & Resorts
  • V Hotel, Curio Collection by Hilton
  • Hilton Dubai Al Habtoor City
  • Metropolitan Hotel Dubai
  • Al Habtoor Polo Resort

Overseas

  • Imperial Hotel, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Vienna (Austria)
  • Hilton London Wembley (United Kingdom)
  • Hilton Beirut Habtoor Grand (Lebanon)
  • Hilton Beirut Metropolitan Palace (Lebanon)
  • President Abraham Lincoln Springfield ‚Äì a DoubleTree by Hilton Hotel (United States)
  • InterContinental Budapest (Hungary)
  • The Ritz-Carlton, Budapest (Hungary)

Al Habtoor Motors' brand portfolio includes Mitsubishi, with a wide choice of sedans, 4x4's and commercial vehicles, two well-known Chinese brands, JAC and Chery, Temsa buses as well as premium marques such as Bentley, McLaren and Bugatti.

The company has a well-established network of nine showrooms, nine service centres, four body shops and ten parts centres that effectively cover the entire UAE. In 2015, Al Habtoor Motors entered the Saudi Arabian market for the first time with Mitsubishi Fuso.

Al Habtoor Motors owns and operates the world‚Äôs first ‚Äì and largest ‚Äì iconic Bentley Motors showroom to be built in major cities around the world. The state-of-the-art showroom is located in a prime location on Sheikh Zayed Road, with built-up area of 76,000 square feet. It consists of three basement floors designated for parking, in addition to three floors of customer area displaying over 70 vehicles, offices, boutiques, Mulliner lounge, a VIP Majlis and other related required services. Adding to its unique design, over 200 thousand LED lights illuminate the outer fa√ßade.

Diamondlease specialises in short-term and long-term leasing of popular brands ranging from small to mid-sized saloons to pick-up trucks and buses.

The Group‚Äôs real estate division includes a variety of commercial and residential properties from office space to luxury villas. Al Habtoor Real Estate provides a total value package, with an emphasis on client needs.

The real estate division includes Al Habtoor City‚Äôs Residence Collection, currently under development. The upmarket lifestyle destination embodies exclusivity and style. The three residential towers comprise of deluxe apartments, lofts and penthouses, ranging from 1-7 bedrooms in a unique neighbourhood. Residents will have access to all Al Habtoor City‚Äôs amenities, which include the largest swimming pool podium in the UAE, a state-of-the-art gym, luxury spa, signature restaurants and have the added bonus of all being right on the banks of the Dubai Water Canal. In addition they can benefit from three five-star hotels right on their doorstep.

The Al Habtoor Group has long been a pioneer in the field of education, it operates two well-established schools offering quality education from KG1 to Grade 13. Emirates International School ‚Äì Jumeirah and Emirates International School ‚Äì The Meadows are accredited IB World Schools.

The Group‚Äôs publishing arm regularly produces quality publications including Al Shindagah magazine, a bilingual corporate magazine, which has been in circulation since1993.

title: Al Habtoor Group
name: Al Habtoor Group
description:
Al Habtoor Grouphas grown with the United Arab Emirates. What started out as a small engineering firm in 1970, is today one of the region‚Äôs most respected conglomerates with interests in the hospitality, automotive, real estate, education and publishing sectors. The Al Habtoor Group has earned itself a solid reputation both locally and internationally due to the vision of its Chairman, Khalaf Ahmad Al Habtoor.

The Al Habtoor Group is one of the UAE's most respected and successful businesses. Today it operates in the UAE and international markets. It employs thousands of highly-qualified, experienced professionals. Just as the name of the UAE has become synonymous with trade and enterprise all over the world, the name of the Al Habtoor Group has become synonymous with dynamic growth, evidenced by its commitment to develop and grow businesses in multiple sectors.

It proudly waves the United Arab Emirates flag in many cities around the globe including London, Vienna, Budapest, Beirut and Springfield, Illinois.

The Group‚Äôs hospitality division includes 14 world-class hotels; seven locally and seven abroad. The portfolio includes:

Dubai, United Arab Emirates

  • Habtoor Grand Resort
  • Waldorf Astoria Dubai Palm Jumeirah
  • Habtoor Palace, LXR Hotels & Resorts
  • V Hotel, Curio Collection by Hilton
  • Hilton Dubai Al Habtoor City
  • Metropolitan Hotel Dubai
  • Al Habtoor Polo Resort

Overseas

  • Imperial Hotel, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Vienna (Austria)
  • Hilton London Wembley (United Kingdom)
  • Hilton Beirut Habtoor Grand (Lebanon)
  • Hilton Beirut Metropolitan Palace (Lebanon)
  • President Abraham Lincoln Springfield ‚Äì a DoubleTree by Hilton Hotel (United States)
  • InterContinental Budapest (Hungary)
  • The Ritz-Carlton, Budapest (Hungary)

Al Habtoor Motors' brand portfolio includes Mitsubishi, with a wide choice of sedans, 4x4's and commercial vehicles, two well-known Chinese brands, JAC and Chery, Temsa buses as well as premium marques such as Bentley, McLaren and Bugatti.

The company has a well-established network of nine showrooms, nine service centres, four body shops and ten parts centres that effectively cover the entire UAE. In 2015, Al Habtoor Motors entered the Saudi Arabian market for the first time with Mitsubishi Fuso.

Al Habtoor Motors owns and operates the world‚Äôs first ‚Äì and largest ‚Äì iconic Bentley Motors showroom to be built in major cities around the world. The state-of-the-art showroom is located in a prime location on Sheikh Zayed Road, with built-up area of 76,000 square feet. It consists of three basement floors designated for parking, in addition to three floors of customer area displaying over 70 vehicles, offices, boutiques, Mulliner lounge, a VIP Majlis and other related required services. Adding to its unique design, over 200 thousand LED lights illuminate the outer fa√ßade.

Diamondlease specialises in short-term and long-term leasing of popular brands ranging from small to mid-sized saloons to pick-up trucks and buses.

The Group‚Äôs real estate division includes a variety of commercial and residential properties from office space to luxury villas. Al Habtoor Real Estate provides a total value package, with an emphasis on client needs.

The real estate division includes Al Habtoor City‚Äôs Residence Collection, currently under development. The upmarket lifestyle destination embodies exclusivity and style. The three residential towers comprise of deluxe apartments, lofts and penthouses, ranging from 1-7 bedrooms in a unique neighbourhood. Residents will have access to all Al Habtoor City‚Äôs amenities, which include the largest swimming pool podium in the UAE, a state-of-the-art gym, luxury spa, signature restaurants and have the added bonus of all being right on the banks of the Dubai Water Canal. In addition they can benefit from three five-star hotels right on their doorstep.

The Al Habtoor Group has long been a pioneer in the field of education, it operates two well-established schools offering quality education from KG1 to Grade 13. Emirates International School ‚Äì Jumeirah and Emirates International School ‚Äì The Meadows are accredited IB World Schools.

The Group‚Äôs publishing arm regularly produces quality publications including Al Shindagah magazine, a bilingual corporate magazine, which has been in circulation since1993.

title: Al Aseel Investments
name: Al Aseel Investments
description:
Al Aseel Investment is a dynamic Saudi Arabian company that has firmly established its presence in various sectors, from textiles and ready-to-wear garments to healthcare. Founded in 1989, the company has grown significantly, expanding its reach and diversifying its offerings to meet evolving market demands.

Initially focusing on the import, export, and trade of textiles, Al Aseel expanded its portfolio through strategic acquisitions, such as the purchase of Al-Jedaie Textiles Company in 2017, which operates over 30 branches across Saudi Arabia. The company‚Äôs entry into the healthcare sector, with a notable SAR 73.1 million medical equipment supply contract in 2020, reflects its forward-thinking approach to business development.

Al Aseel Investment‚Äôs financial performance has seen consistent growth, with sales reaching SAR 78.56 million in the third quarter of 2024, signaling its resilience in a competitive market. The company‚Äôs vision remains focused on providing high-quality products and services while continuously expanding its reach into new sectors, ensuring long-term success and adaptability in an ever-changing global landscape.

title: Gulf Global Group
name: Gulf Global Group
description:
Gulf Global Group was established in 2002 by Arshad Wahedna to invest and consolidate an international asset base. The past 15 years has proved to be an exciting period for its unique growth story having successfully invested, developed, and participated in various joint-venture developments in excess of USD 250 million.

We focus on value added opportunities in the market through our network of industry relationships, with the majority of capital being invested either in land acquisitions for future ground up development, joint venture developments, and private opportunistic developments. Our depth of industry expertise has seen the successful development of 100.000 sq.m of residential and commercial real estate, with and additional 125.000 sq.m currently planned or under construction and slated for completion prior to 2020. In addition to investment and development, a deep understanding in asset management has resulted in value creation for the entire group of stakeholders including investors, tenants and the larger community. We also hold a land bank totaling 175.000 sq.m of allowable area slated for future development.

Our aim is to create a net surplus in social and financial engagement for the built environment through prudent and well planned investment, active management, and transparency.

title: Aswan Developers
name: Aswan Developers
description:
Aswan Developers Inc. was founded by Ashwin Dhamecha, a highly experienced leader in the construction industry, with the aim of delivering high-quality, large-scale infrastructure projects in the UAE and beyond. The company initially gained recognition for its expertise in harbor construction, industrial plants, public utilities, and specialized civil engineering across major cities in India. With its inception in 1974, Aswan expanded its operations to Dubai and Sharjah, marking the beginning of a construction revolution in the rapidly developing UAE.

Over the years, Aswan Developers has built a stellar reputation for integrity and professional excellence. Its ability to deliver on complex projects earned the company the highest level of licensing in the Northern Emirates, enabling it to take on large-scale developments, including tower-rated structures. Aswan's impressive portfolio includes landmark projects such as the Iranian Mosque, Bur Dubai, Dubai Taxi Corp. HQ, and Dubai Tourist Information Centre, solidifying its place as one of the key players in the UAE's construction industry.

With a forward-thinking approach and a keen eye on emerging market trends, Aswan continues to diversify its operations. The company expanded into real estate development, leveraging the UAE's booming property market, and now operates under the umbrella of Aswan Investments and Remaar Real Estate Brokers. Aswan remains committed to exploring new opportunities and contributing to the growth of the UAE's infrastructure landscape.

title: 32 Group Properties
name: 32 Group Properties
description:
32 Group Properties Limited, founded in 1978 by Majid Pishyar, is a dynamic global holding company with diverse business interests across multiple industries. With a history dating back to 1890, the group has established itself as a key player in various sectors, including manufacturing, finance, construction, land development, agricultural projects, and investment management.

The group's companies operate as independent profit centers, granting them the flexibility and autonomy to make efficient decisions even in challenging economic climates. With a strong presence in key economies such as the Americas, Europe, and Asia, as well as emerging regions like the Middle East, Africa, CIS-countries, India, and China, 32 Group leverages its vast global network and experience to connect demand and supply effectively.

32 Group's global reach is underscored by its offices around the world, staffed by a dedicated and knowledgeable team ready to assist clients in expanding their products and services globally. The group's robust financing capabilities ensure secure trade worldwide, offering clients access to a wide array of opportunities for growth and expansion.

Majid Pishyar, the founder and Chairman of 32 Group, has a proven track record of cross-border transactions in various sectors, including real estate, automotive, steel, energy, and more. His extensive experience in advising governmental and multinational companies, as well as facilitating market entries for major brands such as Scania and Mercedes-Benz, highlights his expertise in navigating global business landscapes.

In addition to its focus on real estate transactions in the Middle East, Europe, and North America, 32 Group is active in private equity investments spanning industries such as pharmaceuticals, high-end jewelry, foodstuff, and sports. The group's commitment to excellence and continuous business expansion positions it as a formidable player in the major world economies, driving innovation and growth across its diverse portfolio of businesses.

title: Armada Holding
name: Armada Holding
description:
Armada Holding is a prominent conglomerate based in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia, with a diverse portfolio spanning various industries, including electronics manufacturing, hospitality, healthcare, real estate development, and facilities management. Established in 1998, the company has grown into a significant player in the Middle East's business landscape, operating through multiple subsidiaries and affiliates.

The company's commitment to innovation and quality is evident across its various sectors. In electronics manufacturing, Armada Holding has developed a reputation for producing high-quality products tailored to meet the evolving needs of the market. In the hospitality sector, the company owns and operates hotels and resorts, offering exceptional services and amenities to guests. Armada Holding's real estate development projects are characterized by modern designs and strategic locations, contributing to the urban development of the regions they serve. Additionally, the company's involvement in healthcare and facilities management underscores its dedication to enhancing the quality of life and supporting sustainable development.

Armada Holding's strategic approach focuses on an integrated model encompassing services, trading, and contracting. This approach enables the company to deliver comprehensive solutions across its diverse business units, ensuring reliability in partnerships and client relationships. The company's commitment to prioritizing human well-being among its employees and maintaining eco-conscious practices further reflects its dedication to responsible business operations.

description: ZB Group's commitment to continuous development drives a sophisticated operational approach that delivers exceptional results. title: Star Gigaestablishment
name: Star Gigaestablishment
description:
Star Giga Establishment Limited was formed in Dubai, UAE in 2004 jointly by Mazyood Giga International and ETA Star with a vision to lead in the creation of community styled-living in the region. All the projects undertaken by this union of giants are a study in modern engineering and models for real estate development.

Goldcrest Views 2 and Goldcrest Executive are 39-storey towers that offer a variety of freehold apartments and offices located in Jumeirah Lakes Towers, Dubai. The cost of each project amounts to USD 100 million.

Pearl Residence is a five-tower complex of exclusive freehold properties, at a cost of USD 50 million, developed by incorporating the highest standards of design, construction and luxury and is located in the Emirate of Ajman, UAE.

Goldcrest Dreams are four splendid 30-storey residential towers, at a cost of USD 200 million, located at Emirates City on Emirates Road, Ajman. Emirates City is a multi use project designed to provide fine housing to middle-income families.

Goldcrest Dreams 2 comprises of three towers of 30 floors each at a cost of USD 165 million and is located in the fast rising Emirates City, Emirates Road, Ajman.

title: Emerald Palace Group
name: Emerald Palace Group
description:
Emerald Palace Group (EPG) is an international real estate developer with a legacy dating back to 1996. Over the years, the company has successfully delivered more than 40 large-scale residential projects across Ukraine, the UAE, and Russia, completing over 10,000 homes across more than one million square meters. With a focus on luxury living, EPG continues to expand its presence, with several major developments currently underway.

In Dubai, EPG is renowned for its iconic hospitality and residential assets, including the prestigious Kempinski Hotel & Residences Palm Jumeirah, the opulent Raffles The Palm Dubai, and the lifestyle-focused Hyde Hotel in Business Bay. The group has established strong partnerships with leading global hospitality brands such as Kempinski and Accor, bringing international standards to every project.

EPG operates across various sectors of the real estate industry, offering services in development, construction, project management, interior design, and bespoke fit-outs. With a strong commitment to excellence, EPG has built a reputation for delivering refined, high-quality living environments that reflect both sophistication and timeless style.

title: Safe Developers
name: Safe Developers
description:
Safe Developers is a property development company established by Silgo Group of Companies to build not just property but to build dream Homes.

Even though, Safe Developers is a new company launching its first project, the actual picture is much bigger. Safe Developers is next stage in a natural progression that has been in the making for 35 years. This progression was set in motion by Silgo group, a construction-based group that started with a building maintenance company in UAE in the early 1980s and since been built piece by piece to span several sectors across UAE and India. The promotors are involved in construction, Interior, Manufacturing, Trading, Events and Logistics and offer highly specialized services such as project design advisory, value engineering and Turnkey project solution across UAE and India. Silgo Group has worked with some of the biggest names in the GCC in delivering projects in every sector from industrial, residential, commercial, hospitality and everything in between.

This is the experience that Safe Developers draws from and that is why Safe Developers can confidently claim that it knows what their customers want and deliver it to them with the best quality at the most affordable price.

title: Blue Waters Residential
name: Blue Waters Residential
description:
Blue Waters Residential¬† is a Dubai-based real estate developer known for its involvement in the prestigious Bluewaters Residences project. This development is situated on Bluewaters Island, a man-made island off the coast of Jumeirah Beach Residence, and offers a blend of luxury living with waterfront views. The project is recognized for its contemporary design and premium amenities, catering to residents seeking an upscale lifestyle in Dubai.

The Bluewaters Residences project was completed in 2019 and features 10 mid-rise buildings comprising 698 apartments, 4 penthouses, and 17 townhouses. Each unit is designed with floor-to-ceiling windows, modern interiors, and high-quality finishes. Residents enjoy access to state-of-the-art facilities, including swimming pools, gymnasiums, landscaped gardens, basketball courts, and children's play areas. The development also offers panoramic views of the Arabian Gulf and the iconic Ain Dubai observation wheel.

title: Dubai International Financial Centre
name: Dubai International Financial Centre
description:
The Dubai International Financial Centre (DIFC) is a special economic zone in Dubai covering 110 ha (272 acres), established in 2004 as a financial hub for companies operating throughout the Middle East, Africa, and South Asia (MEASA) markets.

DIFC is regulated by the Dubai Financial Services Authority, an independent regulator exclusive to the zone, and by its own court system, DIFC Courts, separate from the Emirate of Dubai's legal system and that of the federal government of the UAE. DIFC follows the common law framework and operates in English.

DIFC is one of Dubai's independent free zones; it offers companies 100% ownership without the need for a local partner. The freezone houses financial institutions, and wealth funds in addition to retail and hotel space dedicated to the free zones.

DIFC offers clients a 50-year guarantee of zero taxes on corporate income and profits, complemented by the UAE's network of double taxation treaties.

With an uncompromising dedication to quality, our offerings are emblematic of Dubai's prestige - each project is a testament to high-calibre construction and premium finishes that elevate the standards of luxury living.

With the expertise of our in-house mavens in architecture, construction, and project management, we have refined our processes to deliver unparallelled results, ensuring every aspect of our operations exudes sophistication and superiority.

title: Next Realty Real Estate
name: Next Realty Real Estate
description: NEXT is an international brand developing ambitious innovative projects in the markets of Georgia, UAE and Kenya.NEXT's portfolio includes iconic residential and business complexes, 5-star residences created in collaboration with Radisson Hotel Group and Wyndham Hotels and Resorts, luxury resorts, apart-hotels, villas and business centers.

title: Loutraki Real Estate
name: Loutraki Real Estate
description: Loutraki Real Estate L.L.C is a prominent developer that operates as an extension of the renowned Nucorp Constructions group, a well-established entity that has successfully delivered over AUD 500 million worth of projects in the residential and commercial property sectors in Australia since 2011. With over 20 years of collective experience in development and construction, the team at Loutraki Real Estate has earned a solid reputation for delivering high-quality projects.
